                    </figure><!-- .featured-image -->

                    <div class="entry-content">
                        <p>
                            Poverty is one of the main factors that push children into work. Sadiya started working after her father 
                            broke both his arms in a work-related accident. Due to the financial strain on the family, she was forced to quit 
                            school, and found a job in a garment factory.
                        </p>
                    </div><!-- .entry-content -->

